title: Ex d2 midlaner lf team
body:
Tournament experience. Came close to making OPL S4. Won a OCE internet cafe tournament in S5, can play basically any champ worth playing. Shot calling experience.

Haven't played the game in 7 months, not exactly hard to pick back up. If your team is just to play for fun or you lack dedicated members who will show up for practice or events then dont message me.
